  <brief_title>PK Effects of Bifeprunox &amp; Valproate in Bipolar I</brief_title>
  <official_title>Placebo-controlled Study on the Pharmacokinetics,Pharmacodynamics, Safety and Tolerability of Concurrent Valproate and Bifeprunox Administration in Subjects With Bipolar I Disorder</official_title>
